Hello Geeks, I think the issues with VOIP have been asked about multiple times but the comments ranged of what works and what doesn't and with which ISP so I made the below form to survey all the data to hopefully reach a solid conclusion:

https://goo.gl/forms/SbqNrhpJQ5cesEW22

I hope you guys can spare a 2-3 mins to fill it in
#skype #voip #hangouts #messenger #connectionissues #ispissues

I'll share all results in a week isa. 

Thanks for your time
posts.caption: docs.google.com
posts.description: Just surveying what works and what doesn't work. If you have different sets of results and have time, please be kind enough to fill the survey with the other set.
